These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, broccoli, orange, cauliflower
1. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the person eating orange and the person eating cauliflower##7
3. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Food   | orange | broccoli | cauliflower | strawberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, australian, brazilian, american
1. the brazilian is on the right of the american##1
2. the brazilian is somewhere between the australian and the polish##7
3. the brazilian is between the australian and the american##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish | american | brazilian | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, martial-arts, crime, scientific
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | martial-arts | scientific | crime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
