3. the person who likes apricot is somewhere between the person who likes emerald and the person who likes black##7
4. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person who likes emerald##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |
| Color   | black | apricot | blood-red | emerald |

