.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, fuchsia, chestnut, red
1. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##5
2. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes red##7
3. the person who likes red is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2    |      3      |  4  |
| Color   | chestnut | red | fuchsia | blood-red |

 